@startuml JiangMinzhiDetail
title 江民智 jiangminzhi：用户认证、成就与 Web 配置完整类关系

top to bottom direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontName Microsoft YaHei
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam nodesep 55
skinparam ranksep 55
hide empty members
hide circle

skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor<<Controller>> #E8F3FF
  BackgroundColor<<Service>> #EAF7EA
  BackgroundColor<<Mapper>> #FFF4D8
  BackgroundColor<<Entity>> #F7F7F7
  BackgroundColor<<DTO>> #F4EAFE
  BackgroundColor<<Config>> #EFFFF9
  BackgroundColor<<Utility>> #F2F2F2
  BackgroundColor<<Event>> #FFF0F5
  BackgroundColor<<External>> #FFFFFF
}

legend right
  江民智负责：注册登录、JWT、当前用户注解、用户资料、密码修改、Web 配置和成就事件监听。
endlegend

package "江民智负责包 com.hive.jiangminzhi" as JMZ #F4EAFE {
  class "AuthController（认证接口）" as AuthController <<Controller>>
  class "UserController（用户接口）" as UserController <<Controller>>
  class "AchievementController（成就接口）" as AchievementController <<Controller>>

  class "AuthService（认证业务）" as AuthService <<Service>>
  class "UserService（用户业务）" as UserService <<Service>>
  class "AchievementService（成就业务）" as AchievementService <<Service>>

  interface "UserMapper（用户表）" as UserMapper <<Mapper>>
  interface "AchievementMapper（成就表）" as AchievementMapper <<Mapper>>

  class "User（用户实体）" as User <<Entity>>

  class "LoginReq（登录请求）" as LoginReq <<DTO>>
  class "LoginResp（登录响应）" as LoginResp <<DTO>>
  class "RegisterReq（注册请求）" as RegisterReq <<DTO>>
  class "ChangePasswordReq（改密请求）" as ChangePasswordReq <<DTO>>
  class "UpdateProfileReq（资料更新请求）" as UpdateProfileReq <<DTO>>
  class "UserVO（用户响应）" as UserVO <<DTO>>
  class "AchievementVO（成就响应）" as AchievementVO <<DTO>>

  class "JwtUtil（JWT 工具）" as JwtUtil <<Utility>>
  annotation "CurrentUid（当前用户注解）" as CurrentUid
  class "CurrentUidResolver（参数解析器）" as CurrentUidResolver <<Config>>
  class "AuthInterceptor（登录拦截器）" as AuthInterceptor <<Config>>
  class "WebConfig（Web MVC 配置）" as WebConfig <<Config>>

  class "AppEvents（事件容器）" as AppEvents <<Event>>
  class "AppEvents.MessageSent" as MessageSentEvent <<Event>>
  class "AppEvents.ReactionAdded" as ReactionAddedEvent <<Event>>
  class "AppEvents.FriendAccepted" as FriendAcceptedEvent <<Event>>
  class "AppEvents.HiveCreated" as HiveCreatedEvent <<Event>>
  class "AppEvents.DiceRolled" as DiceRolledEvent <<Event>>
  class "AppEvents.UserLoggedIn" as UserLoggedInEvent <<Event>>
}

package "外部依赖：张致硕 zhangzhishuo" as ZZS_EXT #E8F3FF {
  class ApiResponse <<External>>
  class BizException <<External>>
}

package "外部依赖：张凯文 zhangkaiwen" as ZKW_EXT #EAF7EA {
  interface MessageMapper <<External>>
  interface ReactionMapper <<External>>
  class WsPush <<External>>
}

package "外部依赖：虞沛远 yupeiyuan" as YPY_EXT #FFF4D8 {
  interface FriendshipMapper <<External>>
}

AuthController ..> ApiResponse
UserController ..> ApiResponse
AchievementController ..> ApiResponse
UserController ..> CurrentUid
AchievementController ..> CurrentUid

AuthController --> AuthService : 注册登录
AuthService --> UserMapper : 账号持久化
AuthService --> JwtUtil : token 签发
AuthService ..> BizException
AuthService ..> RegisterReq
AuthService ..> LoginReq
AuthService ..> LoginResp
AuthService ..> UserLoggedInEvent : 发布

UserController --> UserService : 资料密码接口
UserService --> UserMapper : 用户持久化
UserService ..> BizException
UserService ..> UserVO
UserController ..> UpdateProfileReq
UserController ..> ChangePasswordReq

AchievementController --> AchievementService : 成就接口
AchievementService --> AchievementMapper : 成就状态
AchievementService --> MessageMapper : 消息统计
AchievementService --> ReactionMapper : 回应统计
AchievementService --> FriendshipMapper : 好友统计
AchievementService --> UserMapper : 用户查询
AchievementService --> WsPush : 成就解锁推送
AchievementService ..> MessageSentEvent : 监听
AchievementService ..> ReactionAddedEvent : 监听
AchievementService ..> FriendAcceptedEvent : 监听
AchievementService ..> HiveCreatedEvent : 监听
AchievementService ..> DiceRolledEvent : 监听
AchievementService ..> UserLoggedInEvent : 监听
AchievementService ..> AchievementVO

WebConfig --> AuthInterceptor : 注册拦截器
WebConfig --> CurrentUidResolver : 注册参数解析器
AuthInterceptor --> JwtUtil : 验证 token
CurrentUidResolver ..> CurrentUid : 解析注解

LoginResp ..> UserVO
UserMapper ..> User
AchievementMapper ..> AchievementVO
AppEvents *-- MessageSentEvent
AppEvents *-- ReactionAddedEvent
AppEvents *-- FriendAcceptedEvent
AppEvents *-- HiveCreatedEvent
AppEvents *-- DiceRolledEvent
AppEvents *-- UserLoggedInEvent

@enduml
